item.title: CoreUI PRO Bootstrap Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1
item.description: We’re proud to announce the release of the CoreUI PRO Bootstrap Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1 on March 23, 2024. This update signifies a comprehensive enhancement across the board, emphasizing our dedication to providing the most efficient, modern, and developer-friendly admin template. From updating scripts to refining the template’s overall responsiveness and layout, v5.0.0-rc.1 is tailored to meet the evolving needs of today’s web developers.
